            "title": "A股收跌   一周累計滬跌深升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股收跌，午後波幅擴大，兩市合計成交23238.29億元(人民幣‧下同)，深股一周累計升逾1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指全日跌11點或0. 3%，報3820，今早也開報3830，跌1點或0.03%，全日最高見3843，升12點或0.31%，後段見3811，跌20點或0.52%，為全日低位，全日成交10163.48億元，一周累計跌36點或0.93%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日跌4點或0.04%，報13070，今早開報13074，跌1點或0.001%，午後高見13182，升107點或0.82%，為全日高位，最低報13016，跌59點或0.45%，為全日低位，全日成交13074.81億元。一周累計升146點或1.13%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日升3點或0.08%，報4501點，今早開報4499點，升1點或0.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日跌4點或0.16%，報3091點，今早開報3098，升3點或0.1%。</p>\n</div>",
