            "title": "A股跌轉升   兩市成交合計近15000億人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日轉升，滬股微跌1點，深股及創板轉升，兩市成交合計14937.51億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指半日跌1點或0.03%，報3830，今早也開報3830，跌1點或0.03%，最高見3838，升7點或0.18%，後段見3813，跌18點或0.47%，為半日低位，半日成交6524億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日升41點或0.32%，報13117，今早開報13074，跌1點或0.001%，最低報13044，跌31點或0.24%，為半日低位，中段高見13172，升97點或0.74%，為半日高位，半日成交8413.51億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日升14點或0.33%，報4512點，今早開報4499點，升1點或0.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日升5點或0.16%，報3100點，今早開報3098，升3點或0.1%。</p>\n</div>",
