            "title": "港股開升38點   勁方首掛飆近116%  晶片股向好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數競價時段開報26583，升38點或0.14% ; 恒生科技指數開報6298，升27點或0.44% ; 恒生國企指數開報9472，升15點或0.17%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交39.11億元。  </p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"勁方醫藥招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/02595.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"勁方醫藥招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/02595.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">勁方醫藥招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">勁方醫藥(02595)首日掛牌，較招股價20.39元勁升115.79%，報44元，成交4.91億元居首。每手賺4722元，該股超購2600倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">網易(09999)回吐3.07%，報233元; 攜程(09961)升1.84%，報609.5元 ; 京東(09618)升2.09%，報137.1元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泡泡瑪特(09992)跌2.25%，報261.2元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯(00981)升2.3%，報71.1元。華虹(01347)升1.64%，報58.9元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紫金(02899)分拆紫金國際，開跌0.85%，報28.06元。</p>\n</div>",
